{
  "stem": "24364.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because I remember I went out quite a few times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We went a couple of times to the movies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Once we had-- we got some money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Our parents somehow managed to get some money to us eventually.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean it took a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "At the beginning we didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember when the guys took me out the first time that the man of the house pulled out 100 crowns and sort of put it in my pocket, I almost died.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because that had never happened to me before in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was always as a child told you can't accept anything from strangers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And when he gave me those 100 crowns, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But eventually, I think-- I remember my parents managed to get some money to me, so I had some money.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And originally I remember I had a friend, sort of an admirer, who used to ask me out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we used to go to various coffee shops and maybe to movies.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And whenever he asked me out, I always said, you know, I don't have any money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I can't pay.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He said, don't worry, I'll write it down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So that went on for a couple of months, and then I got some money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so I went to him, and I said, how much do I owe you, expecting him to say nothing or maybe, I don't know, 10 crowns, or 20 crowns.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "However, he pulled out the piece of paper out of his pocket and said-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
